WEBVTT

00:01.968 --> 00:02.969
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:02.969 --> 00:03.970
Candace: I ONLY KNOW ‐‐
HI.

00:03.970 --> 00:05.038
YOU'RE NOT DRESSED.

00:05.038 --> 00:06.172
LISTEN, I CALLED HIM HERE

00:06.172 --> 00:07.373
'CAUSE I WANT TO TALK.
Hanna: HE'S SELFISH.

00:07.373 --> 00:09.776
HE IS A PLAYER, A HO,
A LIAR, AN ADULTERER.

00:09.776 --> 00:12.212
ALL RIGHT. MOM.
BENNY, YOU ASKED ME.

00:12.212 --> 00:13.880
WHY THE HELL CAN'T YOU KEEP
OUR KIDS IN THE HOUSE?

00:13.880 --> 00:15.381
LISTEN,
YOU ARROGANT BASTARD.

00:15.381 --> 00:16.449
SHE IS GONE.

00:16.449 --> 00:18.184
ARE YOU SLEEPING WITH
OUR CAMPAIGN MANAGER?

00:18.184 --> 00:18.885
NO.

00:18.885 --> 00:20.020
I KNOW THAT HE DID IT,

00:20.020 --> 00:22.388
AND I KNOW THAT YOU ARE
TAMPERING WITH EVIDENCE.

00:22.388 --> 00:23.690
THAT'S WHY YOU'RE
COVERED UP LIKE THIS?

00:23.690 --> 00:24.891
'CAUSE YOU HIDING
FROM THIS MAN?

00:24.891 --> 00:26.026
WHERE IS YOUR BABY,
CANDACE?

00:26.026 --> 00:27.761
YOU KNOW HIM AND QUINCY
GOT INTO IT BEFORE!

00:27.761 --> 00:28.729
WHERE IS YOUR BABY,
CANDACE?

00:28.729 --> 00:30.296
HE'S DEAD!

00:31.965 --> 00:33.734
OH, GOD.

00:33.734 --> 00:36.703
WHAT?

00:40.440 --> 00:42.843
HE'S DEAD, B.

00:42.843 --> 00:44.711
WHAT HAPPENED?

00:46.980 --> 00:49.382
CANDACE,
WHAT HAPPENED TO HIM?

00:49.382 --> 00:51.351
CANDACE,
TELL US.

00:54.788 --> 00:57.891
UM, REMEMBER THAT...

00:57.891 --> 01:00.026
THAT NIGHT
YOU CAME AND FOUND ME...

01:01.868 --> 01:06.640
...AND I WAS BEATEN SO BAD,
YOU CAN BARELY RECOGNIZE ME?

01:13.446 --> 01:14.648
[ SOBS ]

01:14.648 --> 01:17.684
[ Crying ]
I WAS TRYING TO LEAVE HIM.

01:19.085 --> 01:20.320
QUINCY?

01:22.756 --> 01:24.090
YES.

01:26.426 --> 01:27.761
[ SNIFFLES ]

01:27.761 --> 01:29.896
UM...

01:29.896 --> 01:31.431
[ SOBS ]

01:32.566 --> 01:34.635
HE SAID THAT I CAN GO,
BUT...

01:34.635 --> 01:36.069
[ SOBS ]

01:38.304 --> 01:40.240
BUT I COULDN'T
TAKE MY SON.

01:40.240 --> 01:42.809
SO YOU LEFT HIM?

01:44.310 --> 01:46.246
NO.

01:46.246 --> 01:47.848
I...

01:47.848 --> 01:49.382
COULDN'T LEAVE HIM.

01:49.382 --> 01:50.383
[ SNIFFLES ]

01:50.383 --> 01:52.185
THEN WHAT HAPPENED?

01:54.020 --> 01:58.525
QUINCY SAID
THAT HE WANTED $50,000...

01:58.525 --> 02:01.034
OR HE WOULD KILL HIM.

02:05.038 --> 02:07.473
THAT'S WHY YOU ASKED ME
TO MORTGAGE MOMMY'S HOUSE?

02:07.473 --> 02:11.144
[ SOBS ] YEAH.

02:11.144 --> 02:13.179
WHY DIDN'T YOU JUST ASK ME?
WHY DIDN'T YOU JUST TELL ME?

02:13.179 --> 02:15.749
BENNY, THE WAY YOU JUST ACTED,
I COULDN'T.

02:20.821 --> 02:23.356
CANDACE, WHAT HAPPENED
TO MY GRANDBABY?

02:27.160 --> 02:29.963
[ SNIFFLES ]

02:29.963 --> 02:31.798
I GAVE QUINCY THE MONEY.

02:35.936 --> 02:37.771
AND HE TOOK MY SON.

02:40.473 --> 02:42.242
AND HE LEFT.

02:47.681 --> 02:49.783
[ CRYING ]

02:49.783 --> 02:51.284
AND, UM...

02:52.886 --> 02:54.120
...I WAITED.

02:54.120 --> 02:56.356
[ SNIFFLES ]

02:56.356 --> 02:58.659
AND I WAITED.

03:00.767 --> 03:03.103
AND FINALLY,
HE CAME BACK.

03:05.739 --> 03:08.108
AND HE TOLD ME
THAT HE KILLED HIM.

03:09.876 --> 03:10.977
[ SOBS ]

03:13.580 --> 03:15.315
[ SOBS ]

03:15.315 --> 03:16.783
HE...

03:16.783 --> 03:21.622
HE SAID
HE TOOK OUR SON FISHING.

03:21.622 --> 03:23.790
TOLD HIM
THAT HE WAS GONNA GO FISHING.

03:23.790 --> 03:26.259
HE...

03:26.259 --> 03:28.128
HE LOVED TO FISH.

03:30.697 --> 03:33.534
AND HE THREW HIM
OVER A BRIDGE.

03:33.534 --> 03:35.435
[ SNIFFLES ]

03:39.506 --> 03:41.742
AND HE KILLED HIM.

03:47.147 --> 03:50.150
