04:00.026 --> 04:02.603
HE DID THAT?

04:02.603 --> 04:05.739
[ SOBS ]

04:05.739 --> 04:08.108
MM‐HMM.

04:08.108 --> 04:09.475
YEAH.

04:09.475 --> 04:11.011
HE...

04:11.011 --> 04:12.613
YOU KNOW HE'S CRAZY.

04:14.881 --> 04:17.851
LORD HAVE MERCY, CANDACE.

04:22.188 --> 04:25.291
DID YOU TELL THE POLICE?

04:29.930 --> 04:32.365
[ CRYING ]

04:38.572 --> 04:41.542
YES, I DID. AND...

04:45.546 --> 04:47.514
I DID.
I TOLD THEM EVERYTHING.

04:50.517 --> 04:53.486
I GAVE HIM UP
ON ANOTHER MURDER THAT ‐‐

04:53.486 --> 04:56.890
ANOTHER MURDER
THAT HE DID.

04:56.890 --> 04:58.992
[ SNIFFLES ]

04:58.992 --> 05:00.594
YEAH.

05:00.594 --> 05:02.368
AND NOW
HE'S LOOKING FOR ME.

05:04.605 --> 05:05.606
[ SNIFFLES ]

05:05.606 --> 05:07.508
AND HE WANTS...

05:07.508 --> 05:09.342
HE WANTS TO KILL ME.

05:13.747 --> 05:16.550
ALL RIGHT.

05:16.550 --> 05:17.884
YOU'RE GONNA STAY HERE.

05:17.884 --> 05:18.919
BENNY.

05:18.919 --> 05:21.755
MAMA,
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.

05:21.755 --> 05:23.724
[ SNIFFLES ]

05:23.724 --> 05:26.259
SHE WON'T PUT US
IN DANGER AGAIN.

05:26.259 --> 05:27.994
I WON'T HAVE IT.

05:32.365 --> 05:33.600
I'M NOT LETTING HER
LEAVE HERE.

05:33.600 --> 05:35.902
NO.

05:35.902 --> 05:37.203
MAMA.

05:37.203 --> 05:39.405
THIS IS THE LIFE SHE CHOSE,
BENNY.

05:41.107 --> 05:43.610
THAT BOY
IS NOT COMING IN HERE

05:43.610 --> 05:46.046
AND KILLING US ALL
TRYING TO GET TO HER.

05:46.046 --> 05:47.380
SO, WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?
YOU GONNA LET HIM KILL HER?

05:47.380 --> 05:48.515
I DIDN'T SAY THAT.

05:49.816 --> 05:52.318
I GOT A SAFE PLACE TO STAY.
I'M SAFE.

05:52.318 --> 05:54.154
CANDACE,
YOU'RE NOT LEAVING HERE.

05:54.154 --> 05:55.989
YES, SHE IS.

05:55.989 --> 05:58.391
I MEAN,
THIS IS YOUR DAUGHTER.

05:58.391 --> 06:01.134
YES, SHE IS.

06:01.134 --> 06:03.570
AND I TOLD HER
JUST LIKE I TOLD YOU...

06:05.405 --> 06:09.142
...YOU CAN'T GET AWAY
WITH NOTHING IN THIS LIFE.

06:09.142 --> 06:11.978
EVERYTHING YOU DO
IS GONNA COME BACK ON YOU.

06:11.978 --> 06:13.647
YOU MAY THINK
YOU'RE GONNA GET AWAY WITH IT,

06:13.647 --> 06:15.716
BUT YOU REAP WHAT YOU SOW.

06:18.819 --> 06:20.754
YOU MESS AROUND,
AND YOU'LL LOSE IT ALL.

06:22.255 --> 06:24.791
I DON'T KNOW
WHY Y'ALL WON'T LISTEN.

06:26.793 --> 06:29.295
DID YOU HEAR HER?

06:29.295 --> 06:31.932
THAT BOY IS A MURDERER!

06:33.299 --> 06:34.300
I GOT TO GO.

06:34.300 --> 06:35.702
CANDACE...

06:35.702 --> 06:36.770
I MEAN IT, ALL RIGHT?

06:36.770 --> 06:38.104
YOU'RE GONNA STAY HERE.

06:38.104 --> 06:39.706
IT'S OKAY.

06:39.706 --> 06:42.843
COME ON.

06:42.843 --> 06:45.712
BENNY...

06:45.712 --> 06:46.747
LET HER GO.

06:46.747 --> 06:48.582
NO. OKAY?

06:48.582 --> 06:49.583
STOP IT.

06:49.583 --> 06:51.117
SHE'S GONNA STAY HERE.

06:52.853 --> 06:54.354
I'M GONNA LEAVE HERE.

06:54.354 --> 06:56.590
CANDACE, DAMN IT.
I MEAN IT. ALL RIGHT?

06:56.590 --> 06:58.158
NOW SIT YOUR ASS DOWN.

06:58.158 --> 06:59.593
COME HERE.
SIT YOUR ASS DOWN.

07:02.769 --> 07:05.071
NOW, WE'RE FAMILY.

07:05.071 --> 07:06.773
ALL RIGHT?

07:08.809 --> 07:10.410
WE'RE GONNA START ACTING LIKE IT
RIGHT DAMN NOW.

07:10.410 --> 07:12.679
LET'S SIT DOWN.
COME ON. SIT.

07:19.452 --> 07:22.556
BENNY, DON'T GET UPSET.

07:22.556 --> 07:25.225
YOU REMEMBER
WHAT THE DOCTOR SAID, OKAY?

07:27.160 --> 07:29.630
OH, NOW YOU'RE WORRIED
ABOUT WHAT THE DOCTOR SAID?

07:29.630 --> 07:30.631
OH, GIRL.

07:30.631 --> 07:32.498
JUST SHUT UP.

07:37.804 --> 07:40.340
[ Voice breaking ]
BOTH OF YOU.

07:42.509 --> 07:45.445
[ SNIFFLES ]

07:45.445 --> 07:46.880
NOW WE'RE GONNA SIT HERE.
ALL RIGHT?

07:46.880 --> 07:48.782
WE'RE GONNA WATCH SOME TV.

07:51.985 --> 07:54.387
WE'RE GONNA CHILL
LIKE A FAMILY.

07:59.092 --> 08:01.267
Man: <i>FORECAST ‐‐</i>
<i>PLENTY OF SUNSHINE TODAY</i>

08:01.267 --> 08:03.403
<i>WITH SEASONAL TEMPERATURES.</i>

08:09.576 --> 08:10.711
TALK TO ME, DAVID.

08:10.711 --> 08:11.978
DAVID: It's done.

08:11.978 --> 08:12.979
ARE YOU SURE?

08:12.979 --> 08:14.180
Yes.

08:14.180 --> 08:15.949
THEN HOW COME I DON'T SEE IT
ON THE DAMN TELEVISION?

08:15.949 --> 08:18.552
It's done. They're sending
a camera crew there now.

08:18.552 --> 08:20.587
MAKE SURE THAT THEY HURRY,
THEY HURRY.

08:20.587 --> 08:21.655
THE POLICE ARE HERE, JIM.

08:21.655 --> 08:23.189
KATHERYN,
I WANT YOU TO GO UPSTAIRS,

08:23.189 --> 08:25.358
GET WYATT OUT OF HIS ROOM,
AND PUT HIM IN THE KITCHEN.

08:25.358 --> 08:26.727
ARE THEY GOING
TO TAKE HIM?

08:26.727 --> 08:28.795
JUST GET HIM OUT OF HIS ROOM,
PUT HIM IN THE KITCHEN,

08:28.795 --> 08:29.796
TURN THE TELEVISION
ON CHANNEL 17.

08:29.796 --> 08:30.631
BUT ‐‐

08:30.631 --> 08:31.765
I GOT THIS.

08:34.535 --> 08:36.169
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

08:36.169 --> 08:37.638
CHANNEL 17!

08:37.638 --> 08:39.940
CELINE [SIGHS]

08:39.940 --> 08:41.508
PLEASE LET THE CIRCUS
IN THE FRONT DOOR.

08:41.508 --> 08:43.076
YES, SIR.

08:45.512 --> 08:48.014
HERE YOU ARE.

08:48.014 --> 08:51.351
JUDGE WILLA MAPP.

08:51.351 --> 08:53.286
HOW DID I KNOW IT WAS
GONNA BE JUDGE WILLA MAPP?

08:53.286 --> 08:54.988
SEARCH THE HOUSE, GUYS.

08:54.988 --> 08:56.122
YOU SHOULD START
IN THE KITCHEN.

08:56.122 --> 08:57.924
UPSTAIRS.

08:57.924 --> 09:00.594
BUT HE'S IN THE KITCHEN.
WE'LL START UPSTAIRS.

09:00.594 --> 09:02.368
CELINE, WOULD YOU SHOW
THE NICE OFFICERS

09:02.368 --> 09:03.670
UPSTAIRS TO WYATT'S ROOM

09:03.670 --> 09:05.438
AND THEN BRING THEM ALL
DOWN INTO THE KITCHEN

09:05.438 --> 09:07.307
WHERE I'VE ALREADY TOLD
THE D. A. HE IS?

09:07.307 --> 09:09.876
YES, SIR.
THIS WAY, PLEASE.

09:09.876 --> 09:12.178
YOU SHOULD TAKE MY ADVICE.
IT'S A BIG HOUSE.

09:12.178 --> 09:15.682
NOT AS BIG AS THE HOUSE
YOUR SON IS GOING TO.

09:23.624 --> 09:24.725
WHEN YOU'RE DONE UP THERE,

09:24.725 --> 09:27.861
THE SERVANT STEPS
LEAD TO THE KITCHEN!

09:31.898 --> 09:33.800
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

09:33.800 --> 09:35.468
DAD, WHAT'S GOING ON?

09:35.468 --> 09:36.703
IT'S ALMOST OVER, SON.

09:36.703 --> 09:37.971
DAMN IT, KATHERYN.

09:37.971 --> 09:39.906
WHY DON'T YOU HAVE
THE TELEVISION ON CHANNEL 17?!

09:39.906 --> 09:41.374
I LIFTED IT UP.

09:41.374 --> 09:43.009
I JUST DIDN'T HAVE THE CHANCE
TO TURN IT ON YET.

09:43.009 --> 09:44.811
WHAT THE HELL DOES THE TV HAVE
TO DO WITH THIS, ANYWAY, JIM?

09:44.811 --> 09:45.812
JUST...QUIET.

09:45.812 --> 09:47.480
OUR SON
IS ABOUT TO BE ARRESTED.

09:47.480 --> 09:49.516
WOULD YOU LET ME HANDLE IT?
I GOT THIS.

09:49.516 --> 09:51.384
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

09:51.384 --> 09:53.887
A FOOTBALL GAME, JIM?
REALLY?

09:53.887 --> 09:55.121
THERE HE IS.

09:55.121 --> 09:56.523
WYATT CRYER...

09:57.691 --> 09:58.859
...YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

09:58.859 --> 10:00.727
TOLD YOU
HE WAS IN THE KITCHEN.

10:00.727 --> 10:03.169
I GOT HIM...FINALLY.
YEAH. YOU GOT HIM.

10:03.169 --> 10:04.104
JIM.

10:04.104 --> 10:06.039
CAUGHT HIM RED‐HANDED.
STOP IT!

10:06.039 --> 10:08.875
REMIND ME AGAIN WHAT EVIDENCE
YOU HAVE AGAINST MY SON.

10:08.875 --> 10:11.211
BESIDES
YOUR MAID'S TESTIMONY?

10:11.211 --> 10:13.179
YEAH.
LET'S SEE.

10:13.179 --> 10:14.615
HANNA YOUNG

10:14.615 --> 10:17.283
AND THE EYEWITNESS ACCOUNT
OF THE MOTHER OF THE CHILD.

10:17.283 --> 10:19.052
IT'S AIRTIGHT.

10:19.052 --> 10:21.154
MM.

10:21.154 --> 10:23.256
SO WHAT YOU HAVE...

10:23.256 --> 10:24.825
IS A DESCRIPTION.

10:24.825 --> 10:26.092
OH, YES.

10:26.092 --> 10:28.862
AND HIM SHOWING UP
AT THE GRAVESITE DIDN'T HELP.

10:28.862 --> 10:30.664
NO.

10:30.664 --> 10:32.533
YOU'RE WRONG.

10:32.533 --> 10:34.668
MY SON
SHOWING UP AT THE GRAVESITE

10:34.668 --> 10:36.537
OF A LITTLE GIRL
WHO HAD BEEN KILLED

10:36.537 --> 10:38.839
SHOWS HE HAS
GREAT CHARACTER.

10:38.839 --> 10:40.340
SAVE IT FOR COURT.

10:40.340 --> 10:41.708
NO. YOU SAVE IT FOR COURT,
COUNSELOR.

10:41.708 --> 10:43.209
YOU'RE GONNA NEED IT
TO SAVE FACE.

10:43.209 --> 10:44.344
LET'S GO.

10:44.344 --> 10:45.579
[ CELLPHONE BUZZING ]
HANG ON A SECOND.

10:45.579 --> 10:48.214
TAKE HIM.
IS THAT YOUR PHONE...

10:48.214 --> 10:49.550
JENNIFER?

10:49.550 --> 10:50.684
[ BUZZING CONTINUES ]

10:50.684 --> 10:52.653
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

10:52.653 --> 10:54.788
HELLO?

10:57.123 --> 10:58.859
NO.
WE'RE HERE RIGHT NOW.

10:58.859 --> 11:00.093
[ WHISTLE BLOWS ]

11:00.093 --> 11:02.368
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

11:02.368 --> 11:03.537
Reporter:
<i>WE INTERRUPT THIS GAME</i>

11:03.537 --> 11:05.371
<i>TO BRING YOU</i>
<i>THIS BREAKING NEWS.</i>

11:05.371 --> 11:07.541
<i>AUTHORITIES</i>
<i>HAVE MADE THE PUBLIC AWARE</i>

11:07.541 --> 11:09.242
<i>THAT THEY HAVE MADE AN ARREST</i>

11:09.242 --> 11:12.178
<i>IN THE LITTLE LIZZIE</i>
<i>AND BENNY YOUNG HIT AND RUN.</i>

11:12.178 --> 11:14.280
<i>THE MAN'S NAME</i>
<i>IS NORMAN HEWENS.</i>

11:14.280 --> 11:15.649
<i>HE HAS SEVERAL WARRANTS,</i>

11:15.649 --> 11:18.519
<i>AND HE LOOKS</i>
<i>JUST LIKE JUDGE CRYER'S SON.</i>

11:18.519 --> 11:19.853
<i>HE CONFESSED TO THE CRIME,</i>

11:19.853 --> 11:22.188
<i>BUT STILL WON'T REVEAL</i>
<i>WHERE THE CAR IS,</i>

11:22.188 --> 11:23.456
<i>FROM ALL REPORTS HERE.</i>

11:23.456 --> 11:25.692
WOULD YOU FOLKS LIKE TO HAVE
YOUR ICE CREAM NOW

11:25.692 --> 11:28.862
OR AFTER YOU TAKE
THE HANDCUFFS OFF MY SON?

11:30.564 --> 11:34.601
OR PERHAPS YOU'D LIKE
TO JUST GET OUT OF MY HOUSE?

11:34.601 --> 11:36.336
[ HANDCUFFS CLICKING ]

11:38.138 --> 11:39.439
LET'S GO.

11:39.439 --> 11:41.074
CELINE!

11:41.074 --> 11:42.543
Celine: YES, SIR?

11:42.543 --> 11:45.746
PLEASE SHOW THESE NICE PEOPLE
THE FRONT DOOR.

11:45.746 --> 11:46.780
ABSOLUTELY.

11:55.989 --> 11:58.525
THAT IS WHY I WANTED YOU

11:58.525 --> 12:00.834
TO TURN ON
THE DAMN TELEVISION.

12:10.376 --> 12:11.645
Reporter:
<i>...IN THE LITTLE LIZZIE</i>

12:11.645 --> 12:13.479
<i>AND BENNY YOUNG HIT AND RUN.</i>

12:13.479 --> 12:15.716
<i>THE MAN'S NAME</i>
<i>IS NORMAN HEWENS.</i>

12:15.716 --> 12:16.983
<i>HE HAS SEVERAL WARRANTS,</i>

12:16.983 --> 12:19.886
<i>AND HE LOOKS</i>
<i>JUST LIKE JUDGE CRYER'S SON.</i>

12:19.886 --> 12:21.487
<i>HE CONFESSED TO THE CRIME,</i>

12:21.487 --> 12:23.690
<i>BUT STILL WON'T REVEAL</i>
<i>WHERE THE CAR IS,</i>

12:23.690 --> 12:25.425
<i>FROM ALL REPORTS HERE.</i>

12:25.425 --> 12:27.628
<i>THE D. A.'s OFFICE</i>
<i>WILL BE ISSUING AN APOLOGY</i>

12:27.628 --> 12:29.930
<i>TO THE CRYERS AT SOME POINT</i>
<i>LATER THIS EVENING.</i>

12:29.930 --> 12:31.231
<i>BACK TO YOU.</i>

12:31.231 --> 12:33.133
<i>SO, TO RECAP OUR BREAKING NEWS,</i>

12:33.133 --> 12:35.001
<i>POLICE HAVE ARRESTED</i>
<i>NORMAN HEWENS,</i>

12:35.001 --> 12:36.570
<i>WHO HAS CONFESSED</i>
<i>TO THE HIT AND RUN</i>

12:36.570 --> 12:39.172
<i>OF LITTLE LIZZIE</i>
<i>AND BENJAMIN YOUNG.</i>

12:39.172 --> 12:42.075
<i>WE'LL CONTINUE TO FOLLOW</i>
<i>THIS STORY AS IT DEVELOPS.</i>

12:42.075 --> 12:43.076
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

12:43.076 --> 12:44.377
DAD...

12:44.377 --> 12:45.846
HE LOOKS JUST LIKE ME.

12:45.846 --> 12:48.682
YES, HE DOES.

12:48.682 --> 12:50.216
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

12:50.216 --> 12:51.618
BUT HOW?

12:51.618 --> 12:53.854
WYATT...

12:55.656 --> 12:58.124
...IT'S OVER.

12:58.124 --> 12:59.192
LET IT GO.

12:59.192 --> 13:01.167
DAD, I WAS THERE.

13:01.167 --> 13:02.202
WYATT...

13:02.202 --> 13:05.138
IT'S LIKE I SAID
ALL ALONG...

13:05.138 --> 13:07.473
YOU DID NOT DO THIS.

13:07.473 --> 13:10.877
WHO IS THIS GUY?

13:10.877 --> 13:13.914
HE'S NOT YOU.

13:13.914 --> 13:16.650
DON'T LIVE IN THE PAST.

13:16.650 --> 13:19.686
LET'S ALL
JUST GET ON WITH OUR LIVES.

13:28.394 --> 13:30.631
[ TV CLICKS OFF ]

13:32.365 --> 13:34.034
MOM,
HOW DID HE DO THAT?

13:36.503 --> 13:38.171
DO WHAT?

13:53.587 --> 13:54.988
JIM.

13:58.358 --> 13:59.960
HOW DID YOU DO THAT?

14:01.935 --> 14:03.804
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

14:03.804 --> 14:05.405
EXCUSE ME.
DR. LISTEN JUST ARRIVED.

14:05.405 --> 14:06.673
I SHOWED HIM
TO THE LANAI.

14:06.673 --> 14:10.076
I'LL GO GET AMANDA.

14:13.013 --> 14:15.115
BRING SOME TEA
TO THE LANAI, PLEASE.

14:15.115 --> 14:16.182
YES, MA'AM.

14:27.661 --> 14:29.262
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

14:33.233 --> 14:34.400
HEY.

14:34.400 --> 14:36.637
HI.

14:36.637 --> 14:38.038
HOW YOU FEELING, BABY?

14:38.038 --> 14:40.240
GOOD.

14:40.240 --> 14:42.275
AMANDA...

14:44.177 --> 14:45.746
...DR. LISTEN IS HERE.

14:45.746 --> 14:48.882
DO I HAVE
TO SPEAK TO HIM?

14:48.882 --> 14:52.118
I REALLY THINK YOU SHOULD,
HONEY.

14:54.487 --> 14:56.356
OKAY.

14:56.356 --> 14:57.991
OKAY. COME ON.

14:57.991 --> 14:59.292
[ SIGHS ]

14:59.292 --> 15:00.767
OOH.
I LIKE YOUR EARRINGS.

15:00.767 --> 15:02.335
OH, THANKS.

15:17.718 --> 15:21.054
I THINK SHE'S BECOME
A DANGER TO HERSELF AND US.

15:21.054 --> 15:22.956
WHY?

15:22.956 --> 15:24.057
WELL, FOR STARTERS,

15:24.057 --> 15:26.259
SHE TOLD SOMEONE
THAT SHE WANTS TO KILL US.

15:28.995 --> 15:30.296
REALLY?

15:30.296 --> 15:31.297
YES.

15:31.297 --> 15:33.266
NOW, THAT, UH...

15:33.266 --> 15:36.202
I'LL SPEAK TO HER
ABOUT IT.

15:36.202 --> 15:37.604
PLEASE.

15:37.604 --> 15:38.772
FIND OUT WHAT YOU CAN.

15:38.772 --> 15:41.274
VERY DISTURBING.

15:41.274 --> 15:42.643
DR. LISTEN.

15:42.643 --> 15:45.045
HEY.
JUDGE CRYER, HOW ARE YOU?

15:45.045 --> 15:46.747
AH, AMANDA.

15:46.747 --> 15:47.848
DON'T YOU LOOK WELL.

15:47.848 --> 15:49.816
I AM.

15:49.816 --> 15:52.919
HONEY, WHY DON'T WE GO INSIDE,
GIVE THEM A LITTLE PRIVACY?

15:54.254 --> 15:55.822
WE'LL BE
IN THE HOUSE.

15:55.822 --> 15:57.591
THANK YOU.

16:04.270 --> 16:06.306
IT'S GOOD TO SEE YOU.

16:29.830 --> 16:32.966
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

16:32.966 --> 16:34.000
[ SIGHS ]

16:34.000 --> 16:35.736
I HOPE THIS HELPS.

16:37.571 --> 16:38.939
[ SNIFFS ]

16:38.939 --> 16:41.307
I'M SURE IT WILL.

16:43.309 --> 16:45.011
HOW DID YOU DO IT?

16:47.180 --> 16:48.715
DO WHAT?

16:48.715 --> 16:51.552
THE WYATT LOOK‐ALIKE.

16:54.888 --> 16:57.958
YOU CAN THANK ME LATER.

17:00.433 --> 17:02.235
NO.

17:04.605 --> 17:06.206
I THINK
I'LL THANK YOU NOW.

17:06.206 --> 17:09.109
[ GRUNTS ]

17:12.679 --> 17:17.483
YOU ARE
AN EVIL, SELFISH BASTARD...

17:17.483 --> 17:20.621
AND A HORRIBLE HUSBAND.

17:22.155 --> 17:23.524
YOU MAKE ME UNHAPPY

17:23.524 --> 17:26.660
EVERY DAY
I AM IN YOUR PRESENCE.

17:28.461 --> 17:31.164
YOU ARE SELF‐RIGHTEOUS...

17:31.164 --> 17:33.734
A SOCIOPATH...

17:33.734 --> 17:36.169
AND AN ALL‐AROUND
SON OF A BITCH.

17:40.340 --> 17:42.743
BUT YOU LOVE
YOUR CHILDREN.

17:44.778 --> 17:47.380
YOU WILL DO ANYTHING
TO PROTECT THEM,

17:47.380 --> 17:51.384
EVEN IF IT'S
TO THEIR OWN DETRIMENT.

17:55.488 --> 17:58.825
I HOPE YOU ARE READY

17:58.825 --> 18:02.368
FOR THE MILLION
LITTLE PIECES

18:02.368 --> 18:06.072
THAT THEY ARE BOTH
GOING TO FALL INTO.

18:09.810 --> 18:13.246
YOU HAVE PROTECTED THEM...

18:13.246 --> 18:16.717
RIGHT INTO INSANITY.

18:19.720 --> 18:23.056
CONGRATULATIONS.

18:23.056 --> 18:26.560
AND THANK YOU.

18:33.199 --> 18:34.835
[ GLASS THUDS ]

18:37.270 --> 18:39.740
[ LIQUID POURING ]

18:51.585 --> 18:53.319
[ SIGHS ]

18:54.755 --> 18:56.957
YOU'RE WELCOME.

19:12.045 --> 19:15.215
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

19:15.215 --> 19:16.416
CARLOS.

19:16.416 --> 19:17.518
YES, SIR.

19:17.518 --> 19:18.952
CAN YOU DELIVER THESE
TO JUDGE CRYER'S HOUSE?

19:18.952 --> 19:19.953
HE NEEDS THEM.

19:19.953 --> 19:21.522
JUDGE CRYER'S HOUSE?
YES.

19:21.522 --> 19:22.823
HERE IS THE ADDRESS
RIGHT HERE.

19:22.823 --> 19:24.024
OKAY.

19:24.024 --> 19:25.058
COOL?

19:25.058 --> 19:26.092
YEAH.
OKAY.

19:26.092 --> 19:27.127
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

19:36.837 --> 19:38.104
HEY.
HI.

19:38.104 --> 19:39.540
MY DAD HERE?
YES.

19:39.540 --> 19:40.541
OKAY.

19:40.541 --> 19:42.475
I'M SORRY
ABOUT THIS MORNING.

19:44.645 --> 19:46.279
DON'T MENTION IT.

19:46.279 --> 19:48.815
I WANT TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

19:51.151 --> 19:53.053
I DON'T THINK SO.

19:57.490 --> 20:00.767
YES. WELL,
I NEED TO CALL YOU BACK.

20:00.767 --> 20:04.370
FINE. THANK YOU.

20:04.370 --> 20:05.839
HEY.

20:05.839 --> 20:07.073
HOW ARE YOU, SON?

20:07.073 --> 20:08.909
I'M GOOD.

20:12.646 --> 20:14.981
SO, YOU WANTED TO SEE ME?

20:14.981 --> 20:16.950
YES, YES.

20:16.950 --> 20:18.451
HAVE A SEAT.

20:25.358 --> 20:26.693
UM...

20:28.461 --> 20:31.732
I'M SORRY
ABOUT THIS MORNING.

20:31.732 --> 20:34.500
THAT'S FINE.

20:34.500 --> 20:37.337
WHAT WERE ‐‐
WHAT WERE YOU DOING THERE?

20:37.337 --> 20:41.508
I HAD AN EARLY MEETING
WITH MAGGIE.

20:43.376 --> 20:45.145
[ SIGHS ]

20:45.145 --> 20:47.648
WHY WERE YOU
IN LANDON'S ROOM?

20:50.383 --> 20:53.153
I MET HIM LAST WEEK,
AND HE WAS ‐‐ HE WAS...

20:53.153 --> 20:54.821
HE WAS REALLY NICE TO ME.

20:56.222 --> 20:58.391
BEFORE YOU MET HIM HERE?

20:58.391 --> 21:00.667
YES.

21:00.667 --> 21:02.168
WHERE?

21:04.738 --> 21:06.339
AT A BAR.

21:08.274 --> 21:10.176
GAY BAR.

21:15.782 --> 21:17.818
UH...

21:17.818 --> 21:22.355
I'M SORRY THAT I EMBARRASSED YOU
THIS ‐‐ THIS MORNING

21:22.355 --> 21:23.590
IN FRONT OF MS. DAY.

21:23.590 --> 21:24.791
EMBARRASS ME?
YEAH.

21:24.791 --> 21:26.560
YEAH.
AND I WON'T GO BACK AGAIN.

21:26.560 --> 21:29.129
YOU THINK
YOU EMBARRASS ME?

21:29.129 --> 21:31.131
OF COURSE,
AND THAT'S WHY I'M TELLING YOU

21:31.131 --> 21:34.067
THAT I WON'T GO BACK
TO THAT GAY BAR AGAIN.

21:34.067 --> 21:35.401
WHY NOT?

21:37.270 --> 21:39.606
I KNOW
YOU'RE NOT HAPPY ABOUT THIS.

21:39.606 --> 21:41.675
[ SIGHS ]

21:41.675 --> 21:43.109
YOU'RE MISTAKEN.

21:43.109 --> 21:45.245
COME ON, DAD.
YOU DON'T HAVE TO PRETEND.

21:45.245 --> 21:46.312
I...

21:46.312 --> 21:47.347
I KNOW.

21:47.347 --> 21:50.150
I'M A BIG DISAPPOINTMENT
TO YOU.

21:50.150 --> 21:52.385
YOU ARE WRONG.

21:54.487 --> 21:57.357
NOW,
YOU LISTEN TO ME, SON.

21:58.925 --> 22:01.234
YOU ARE A GROWN MAN.

22:03.269 --> 22:05.672
YOU ARE
NOT AN EMBARRASSMENT.

22:06.907 --> 22:10.877
I LOVE YOU VERY MUCH.

22:10.877 --> 22:13.213
NOW, TO ME,

22:13.213 --> 22:16.883
THE FACT
THAT YOU ARE GAY...

22:16.883 --> 22:21.054
IS...IT'S LIKE
YOUR HAIR BEING BLACK

22:21.054 --> 22:24.825
OR YOU'RE 6 FEET TALL

22:24.825 --> 22:25.859
OR YOUR EYES
ARE DARK BROWN.

22:25.859 --> 22:26.860
THEY...

22:26.860 --> 22:29.462
THEY ARE
YOUR CHARACTERISTICS

22:29.462 --> 22:31.497
THAT MAKE YOU
WHO YOU ARE.

22:31.497 --> 22:32.999
YOU ARE MY SON.

22:37.003 --> 22:38.471
YOU DO NOT EMBARRASS ME,

22:38.471 --> 22:40.040
AND I DON'T WANT YOU
TO BE EMBARRASSED

22:40.040 --> 22:42.843
THAT YOU ARE GAY
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.

22:47.581 --> 22:49.049
SO...

22:49.049 --> 22:53.153
I MEAN, YOU DON'T CARE THAT
I WAS IN THE ROOM WITH LANDON?

22:55.088 --> 22:57.357
I DON'T WANT
TO KNOW THE DETAILS.

22:57.357 --> 23:00.834
[ CHUCKLES ] NO.
WE DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.

23:00.834 --> 23:02.703
OKAY.

23:02.703 --> 23:05.438
WELL...

23:05.438 --> 23:07.373
I SUPPOSE
I SHOULD MAKE AN EFFORT

23:07.373 --> 23:08.609
TO GET TO KNOW HIM.

23:08.609 --> 23:09.643
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:09.643 --> 23:11.411
IT'S ‐‐
IT'S NOT LIKE THAT.

23:11.411 --> 23:13.547
I MEAN,
HE'S JUST A FRIEND.

23:13.547 --> 23:15.315
OKAY.

23:15.315 --> 23:17.383
THAT'S GOOD.

23:19.520 --> 23:21.354
SO YOU DON'T CARE?

23:21.354 --> 23:24.290
I CARE ABOUT <i>YOU.</i>

23:24.290 --> 23:26.960
I DON'T CARE
THAT YOU'RE GAY.

23:26.960 --> 23:29.095
I WANT YOU
TO BE HAPPY AND FREE

23:29.095 --> 23:30.731
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.

23:38.138 --> 23:40.641
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:40.641 --> 23:43.076
WELL, MOM SURE DOES CARE.

23:43.076 --> 23:44.611
YES.

23:44.611 --> 23:45.846
[ SIGHS ]

23:45.846 --> 23:48.048
WE JUST...

23:48.048 --> 23:51.217
WE NEED TO GIVE YOUR MOTHER
SOME TIME.

23:51.217 --> 23:54.655
SHE DOESN'T WANT ME
TO BE FREE, DAD.

23:54.655 --> 23:56.056
I'LL TALK TO HER.

23:56.056 --> 24:00.360
NO. SHE'S NOT GONNA
CHANGE HER MIND.

24:00.360 --> 24:01.735
SHE HAS THE CAR.

24:01.735 --> 24:04.805
SHE'S GONNA TURN ME IN
IF I DON'T DO WHAT SHE WANTS.

24:04.805 --> 24:06.673
SHE IS NOT GOING
TO TURN YOU IN.

24:06.673 --> 24:08.675
DAD, DAD, SHE WILL.

24:08.675 --> 24:11.177
NO, SHE WON'T.

24:11.177 --> 24:15.348
I WILL TALK TO HER AGAIN.

24:15.348 --> 24:19.653
I WANT YOU TO BE FREE.

24:22.255 --> 24:23.624
YOU'LL GET THE CAR?

24:23.624 --> 24:26.693
I AM TRYING.
I WILL GET IT.

24:28.094 --> 24:31.632
UNTIL YOU DO...

24:31.632 --> 24:33.800
I CAN'T BE FREE.

24:36.302 --> 24:39.540
YEAH.

24:39.540 --> 24:41.174
[ SIGHS ]

24:41.174 --> 24:43.243
[ SIGHS ]

25:02.769 --> 25:04.337
NO AGITATION?

25:04.337 --> 25:06.372
SOME.

25:06.372 --> 25:09.342
WHY DO YOU THINK
THAT IS?

25:09.342 --> 25:10.944
NO ONE
WILL LEAVE ME ALONE.

25:10.944 --> 25:12.546
WHO?

25:12.546 --> 25:14.615
MY MOM AND DAD.

25:14.615 --> 25:16.517
WHAT WOULD
YOU LIKE THEM TO DO?

25:16.517 --> 25:18.985
GO AWAY.

25:18.985 --> 25:20.453
HOW SO?

25:20.453 --> 25:23.323
I JUST WANT THEM
TO LEAVE ME ALONE.

25:23.323 --> 25:26.560
YOU WANT THEM
OUT OF THE PICTURE?

25:26.560 --> 25:28.294
YES.

25:28.294 --> 25:31.297
HOW FAR AWAY?

25:31.297 --> 25:34.835
FAR ENOUGH AWAY
THAT I CAN BE BY MYSELF...

25:34.835 --> 25:36.637
LIVE MY OWN LIFE.

25:36.637 --> 25:39.673
YOU KNOW,
SOMETIMES PEOPLE'S PARENTS DIE,

25:39.673 --> 25:40.741
AND THEY REGRET ‐‐

25:40.741 --> 25:43.276
I DON'T WANT THEM TO DIE.

25:43.276 --> 25:46.179
THAT'S INSANE.

25:46.179 --> 25:47.247
YOU DON'T?

25:47.247 --> 25:48.715
NO.

25:52.686 --> 25:54.487
OKAY.

25:54.487 --> 25:55.722
OKAY.

25:55.722 --> 25:58.692
GOOD.

25:58.692 --> 25:59.860
GOOD.

25:59.860 --> 26:01.735
TAKING YOUR MEDS?
YES.

26:01.735 --> 26:04.104
HEARING ANY VOICES?
NO.

26:04.104 --> 26:05.371
HOW ARE YOU SLEEPING?

26:05.371 --> 26:06.973
FINE.

26:08.675 --> 26:11.011
OKAY.

26:11.011 --> 26:14.480
I'M TELLING EVERYONE
I'M GOOD,

26:14.480 --> 26:16.517
BUT I JUST WANT THEM
TO LEAVE ME ALONE.

26:19.252 --> 26:20.721
I'LL TALK
TO YOUR PARENTS.

26:20.721 --> 26:21.722
PLEASE.

27:29.495 --> 27:31.497
DAMN IT!

27:45.311 --> 27:46.312
[ DOOR OPENS ]

27:46.312 --> 27:47.881
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

27:47.881 --> 27:48.949
AMANDA.

27:48.949 --> 27:50.050
WHY ARE YOU IN HERE?

27:50.050 --> 27:52.953
YOU KNOW
I ALWAYS CHECK UP ON CELINE.

27:52.953 --> 27:53.820
FOR WHAT?

27:53.820 --> 27:57.691
TO MAKE SURE
SHE'S DOING HER JOB.

27:57.691 --> 27:59.593
GET OUT OF MY ROOM,
PLEASE.

28:03.436 --> 28:05.205
OKAY.

28:05.205 --> 28:06.272
NOW!

28:08.074 --> 28:09.710
IS DR. LISTEN DOWNSTAIRS?

28:09.710 --> 28:11.678
YES.

28:11.678 --> 28:12.679
WELL, WHAT DID HE SAY?

28:12.679 --> 28:15.115
I'M FINE, MEENIE.

28:17.483 --> 28:18.552
WHAT'S "MEENIE"?

28:18.552 --> 28:19.753
YOU.

28:19.753 --> 28:23.990
IS THAT A NEW NICKNAME?

28:23.990 --> 28:26.026
MM‐HMM.

28:26.026 --> 28:28.261
OKAY.

28:28.261 --> 28:30.564
GET OUT.

28:44.745 --> 28:46.513
BYE, MOM.

28:58.324 --> 29:00.226
[ GUN COCKS ]

29:00.226 --> 29:03.136
♪♪ EENIE, MEENIE, MINEY, MOE ♪♪

29:03.136 --> 29:06.940
♪♪ EENIE, MEENIE, MINEY, MOE ♪♪

29:06.940 --> 29:10.744
♪♪ EENIE, MEENIE, MINEY, MOE ♪♪

29:12.713 --> 29:15.215
♪♪ EENIE, MEENIE, MINEY, MOE ♪♪

29:17.183 --> 29:18.952
WHAT I'M
MOST CONCERNED ABOUT

29:18.952 --> 29:20.554
IS THIS WHOLE...

29:20.554 --> 29:21.822
BOYFRIEND THING.

29:21.822 --> 29:23.189
WHAT'S UP WITH
THE WHOLE BOYFRIEND THING?

29:23.189 --> 29:24.457
AH, SHE NEVER MENTIONED IT
TO ME.

29:24.457 --> 29:25.425
AND YOU DIDN'T ASK HER?

29:25.425 --> 29:27.594
I DIDN'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT IT.

29:27.594 --> 29:30.330
WHY DO YOU THINK SHE WOULDN'T
MENTION THAT TO YOU?

29:30.330 --> 29:33.867
SOMETIMES PATIENTS LIKE
TO KEEP THINGS TO THEMSELVES.

29:33.867 --> 29:35.736
IT'S HUMAN NATURE.

29:35.736 --> 29:39.506
HOW CAN A...

29:39.506 --> 29:41.642
HOW CAN A FATHER

29:41.642 --> 29:44.310
KNOW WHEN HIS DAUGHTER'S
KEEPING SOMETHING FROM HIM?

29:44.310 --> 29:47.080
SHE NEVER KEEPS
THE DARK THINGS FROM ME.

29:47.080 --> 29:49.249
SHE'S FINE.
SHE REALLY IS.

29:49.249 --> 29:50.984
REALLY?

29:50.984 --> 29:52.653
YES, YES.
SHE'S FINE.

29:52.653 --> 29:53.887
THANKS, DOC.
I'LL TELL KATHERYN.

29:53.887 --> 29:54.921
[ DOOR OPENS ]
GOOD.

29:54.921 --> 29:55.922
GOOD.
TELL ME WHAT?

29:55.922 --> 29:57.057
OH.
OH.

29:57.057 --> 29:58.358
AMANDA'S FINE.

29:58.358 --> 30:00.060
IS SHE?
YES. SHE IS.

30:00.060 --> 30:01.868
I WAS TALKING TO THE DOCTOR,
JIM.

30:01.868 --> 30:03.403
YES.
SHE SEEMS FINE.

30:03.403 --> 30:05.038
ARE YOU SURE?

30:05.038 --> 30:08.041
YES. BUT I AM GONNA UP
HER ANXIETY MEDS,

30:08.041 --> 30:11.745
AND I'M GONNA PRESCRIBE
SOMETHING FOR HER TO SLEEP.

30:11.745 --> 30:15.982
SHE SAYS SHE'S SLEEPING FINE,
BUT I THINK SHE LOOKS TIRED.

30:15.982 --> 30:17.918
YEAH.
YEAH.

30:17.918 --> 30:19.620
WELL, DO ALL YOU CAN FOR HER.
I APPRECIATE IT.

30:19.620 --> 30:20.654
I CERTAINLY WILL.

30:20.654 --> 30:21.655
THANK YOU.
PLEASURE.

30:21.655 --> 30:22.656
THANK YOU, THANK YOU.
THANK YOU.

30:22.656 --> 30:25.491
WE'LL TAKE CARE OF IT.
YEAH.

30:25.491 --> 30:28.695
AS I TOLD YOU,
AMANDA IS FINE.

30:28.695 --> 30:30.363
WELL, SOMETIMES ‐‐
IT'S GUN SMOKE.

30:30.363 --> 30:31.932
IT ‐‐

30:33.567 --> 30:34.601
HELLO.

30:35.936 --> 30:37.904
WHAT IN THE HELL ARE YOU
DOING ON MY PROPERTY?

30:37.904 --> 30:39.873
I KNOW YOU SAID
YOU WON'T ACCEPT MY APOLOGY,

30:39.873 --> 30:41.908
AND I UNDERSTAND THAT,
BUT I NEED TO.

30:41.908 --> 30:43.176
I'M SORRY.

30:43.176 --> 30:45.178
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA

30:45.178 --> 30:46.780
HOW MUCH TROUBLE
YOU CAUSED MY SON?

30:46.780 --> 30:47.781
ANY AT ALL?
I KNOW.

30:47.781 --> 30:48.782
OH. YOU KNOW?

30:48.782 --> 30:50.751
YOU NEED TO LEAVE,
HANNA.

30:50.751 --> 30:52.152
YOU NEED TO LEAVE NOW.
I KNOW YOU SAID

30:52.152 --> 30:54.154
YOU WON'T ACCEPT MY APOLOGY,
AND I ACCEPT THAT.

30:54.154 --> 30:55.288
GOOD.

30:55.288 --> 30:56.957
I WILL NOT ACCEPT
YOUR APOLOGY.

30:56.957 --> 30:58.491
BUT I ‐‐
YOU NEED TO LEAVE, HANNA.

30:58.491 --> 31:01.301
YOU NEED TO LEAVE NOW.
HANNA.

31:01.301 --> 31:02.669
OH, KATHERYN. PLEASE, DON'T,
NO. REALLY?

31:02.669 --> 31:05.371
STOP IT.

31:05.371 --> 31:06.372
[ GROANS ]

31:06.372 --> 31:08.041
MRS. CRYER, I'M SORRY.

31:08.041 --> 31:10.110
I AM SO SORRY.

31:10.110 --> 31:11.211
HANNA, IT IS SO GOOD
TO SEE YOU.

31:11.211 --> 31:12.212
NO. PLEASE.

31:12.212 --> 31:14.014
PLEASE LET ME
JUST SAY THIS.

31:14.014 --> 31:16.950
I, UH...

31:16.950 --> 31:19.152
I WAS JUST SO BOTHERED
BY WHAT HAPPENED WITH BENNY

31:19.152 --> 31:21.187
AND ALL OF THIS,
I COULDN'T EVEN THINK STRAIGHT.

31:21.187 --> 31:22.856
WE HEAR YOU, HANNA.
YOU NEED TO LEAVE.

31:22.856 --> 31:24.390
I NEED TO APOLOGIZE
TO WYATT.

31:24.390 --> 31:26.126
NO. YOU DO NOT NEED
TO SPEAK TO WYATT.

31:26.126 --> 31:28.061
YOU NEED TO LEAVE
THE PROPERTY NOW!

31:28.061 --> 31:30.564
BUT IT RUINED HIS LIFE.
HANNA, PLEASE.

31:30.564 --> 31:32.165
IT IS FINE.

31:32.165 --> 31:34.500
I AM SO SORRY.

31:34.500 --> 31:38.138
I WAS BLINDED
BY ALL OF THIS.

31:38.138 --> 31:39.372
I'M JUST SO SORRY.

31:39.372 --> 31:41.174
I WAS BLINDED
BY EVERYTHING.

31:41.174 --> 31:42.609
KATHERYN,
IT IS NOT FINE.

31:42.609 --> 31:44.177
WE HEAR YOU, HANNA.

31:44.177 --> 31:45.478
CAN YOU LEAVE NOW?

31:45.478 --> 31:46.479
PLEASE.

31:46.479 --> 31:47.848
JIM, JUST STOP IT, OKAY?

31:47.848 --> 31:49.716
LOOK, MRS. CRYER ‐‐

31:49.716 --> 31:51.284
WHAT THE HELL IS IT WITH YOU?
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

31:51.284 --> 31:52.886
GO IN THE DAMN HOUSE.
I'M GOING IN THE DAMN HOUSE.

31:52.886 --> 31:53.887
NOW!

31:53.887 --> 31:55.021
YOU NEED TO GET OFF
MY PROPERTY.

32:00.226 --> 32:01.467
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
MRS. CRYER,

32:01.467 --> 32:04.571
I DON'T WANT TO BE A PROBLEM
FOR YOU AND YOUR HUSBAND.

32:04.571 --> 32:08.575
HANNA, MY PROBLEM
STARTED AT "I DO."

32:08.575 --> 32:10.877
[ CHUCKLES ]

32:10.877 --> 32:11.912
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

32:11.912 --> 32:13.747
I AM SO SORRY.

32:16.416 --> 32:18.051
HOW'S BENNY?

32:18.051 --> 32:21.021
[ Chuckling ] OH.

32:21.021 --> 32:24.390
YOU PROBABLY KNOW THIS
ALREADY, BUT...

32:24.390 --> 32:26.059
HE'S AWAKE.

32:26.059 --> 32:27.427
OH.

32:27.427 --> 32:28.562
[ Voice breaking ]
HE'S WALKING.

32:28.562 --> 32:29.630
HE'S FINE.

32:29.630 --> 32:30.964
HE'S AT HOME.

32:30.964 --> 32:33.366
HE'S REALLY GOOD.

32:33.366 --> 32:35.235
I'M SO HAPPY.

32:35.235 --> 32:38.071
YEAH. BUT...

32:38.071 --> 32:40.040
[ SIGHS ]

32:40.040 --> 32:41.942
I'M THROWING A SURPRISE PARTY
FOR HIM TONIGHT,

32:41.942 --> 32:43.443
AND HE DOESN'T
EVEN KNOW IT.

32:43.443 --> 32:45.746
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

32:45.746 --> 32:47.514
BUT I COULDN'T LET
THE SUN GO DOWN

32:47.514 --> 32:49.616
WITHOUT ASKING YOU
TO FORGIVE ME.

32:49.616 --> 32:50.784
THERE'S NO NEED FOR THAT.

32:50.784 --> 32:51.785
PLEASE.

32:51.785 --> 32:54.120
PLEASE.

32:54.120 --> 32:56.256
PLEASE FORGIVE ME.

32:59.025 --> 33:01.467
ALL IS FORGIVEN, HANNA.

33:01.467 --> 33:03.203
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:03.203 --> 33:06.940
I JUST WANT TO PUT
ALL OF THIS BEHIND US.

33:06.940 --> 33:08.809
HOW'S WYATT?

33:08.809 --> 33:11.645
HE'S GOOD.

33:11.645 --> 33:14.815
CAN WE TALK
WHEN YOU COME BACK TO WORK?

33:14.815 --> 33:17.350
WHAT?

33:17.350 --> 33:20.486
PLEASE.

33:20.486 --> 33:23.524
YOU WANT
TO GIVE ME MY JOB BACK.

33:26.259 --> 33:28.595
MRS. CRYER, I DON'T EVEN
KNOW HOW TO REPAY YOU.

33:31.197 --> 33:35.368
YOU MOVED BENNY,
YOU TOOK CARE OF HIS BILL,

33:35.368 --> 33:39.005
AND YOU WANT TO GIVE ME
MY JOB BACK.

33:39.005 --> 33:41.041
MM, MM, MM.

33:41.041 --> 33:42.442
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

33:44.911 --> 33:47.113
THANK YOU.
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:47.113 --> 33:49.850
DON'T MENTION IT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:49.850 --> 33:52.118
BUT WHAT ABOUT MR. CRYER?

33:52.118 --> 33:54.588
I CAN HANDLE HIM.

33:54.588 --> 33:58.191
[ LAUGHS ]

33:58.191 --> 34:00.567
ARE YOU SURE ABOUT THIS?

34:00.567 --> 34:02.335
YES.

34:04.905 --> 34:06.673
NOW...

34:06.673 --> 34:09.576
WHEN CAN YOU START BACK?

34:09.576 --> 34:11.578
[ LAUGHS ]

34:11.578 --> 34:13.246
WHEN DO YOU WANT ME BACK?

34:13.246 --> 34:16.683
WELL...

34:16.683 --> 34:17.851
GET BENNY SETTLED.

34:17.851 --> 34:20.120
YEAH.

34:20.120 --> 34:22.889
AND WHEN YOU'RE READY,
COME BACK AFTER THAT.

34:22.889 --> 34:24.758
CELINE
IS DRIVING ME INSANE.

34:24.758 --> 34:26.092
[ LAUGHS ]

34:26.092 --> 34:29.029
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:29.029 --> 34:30.731
OKAY. [ LAUGHS ]

34:30.731 --> 34:32.999
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?

34:32.999 --> 34:35.235
YOU SHOULD COME BY
TO BENNY'S PARTY TONIGHT.

34:35.235 --> 34:36.903
I WANT YOU TO MEET HIM.

34:39.139 --> 34:40.140
REALLY?

34:40.140 --> 34:41.875
YEAH.

34:41.875 --> 34:43.677
COULD YOU DO THAT?

34:43.677 --> 34:45.411
I'D LIKE THAT VERY MUCH.

34:45.411 --> 34:47.581
[ LAUGHS ]

34:47.581 --> 34:48.949
TEXT ME THE ADDRESS.

34:48.949 --> 34:51.217
I WILL.

34:51.217 --> 34:52.519
THANK YOU.

34:59.926 --> 35:01.167
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:01.167 --> 35:02.168
OH, SORRY.

35:02.168 --> 35:03.704
[ LAUGHS ]

35:03.704 --> 35:04.938
SEE YOU LATER.

35:04.938 --> 35:07.107
TAKE CARE. YES.

35:23.289 --> 35:26.092
IF YOU THINK FOR ONE MINUTE
THAT THAT WOMAN

35:26.092 --> 35:28.595
IS EVER STEPPING A FOOT
IN THIS HOUSE AGAIN,

35:28.595 --> 35:29.696
YOU ARE SORELY MISTAKEN.

35:29.696 --> 35:30.964
OH, SHE'S STEPPING A FOOT

35:30.964 --> 35:32.065
IN THIS HOUSE, ALL RIGHT,

35:32.065 --> 35:33.700
BECAUSE SHE'S COMING
BACK TO WORK.

35:33.700 --> 35:35.235
WHAT IN THE HELL IS IT
WITH YOU TWO?

35:35.235 --> 35:36.670
SHE IS A FRIEND.

35:36.670 --> 35:38.404
SHE'S A FRIEND?
YES.

35:38.404 --> 35:39.840
A FRIEND
WHO TURNED IN YOUR SON.

35:39.840 --> 35:41.174
WELL, YOU HANDLED THAT,
NOW, DIDN'T YOU?

35:41.174 --> 35:42.776
YES, I DID!
I HANDLED IT FINE.

35:42.776 --> 35:43.810
I HANDLED IT WITHOUT YOU,

35:43.810 --> 35:45.546
AND I CERTAINLY HANDLED IT
WITHOUT HER.

35:45.546 --> 35:47.047
SHE'S COMING BACK TO WORK.

35:47.047 --> 35:49.082
SHE COMES BACK TO WORK,
AND I PROMISE YOU,

35:49.082 --> 35:51.852
I WILL MAKE EVERY MOMENT
SHE IS HERE A LIVING HELL.

35:51.852 --> 35:52.953
WELL,
THEN WHY DON'T YOU START

35:52.953 --> 35:54.354
WITH THAT WHORE
IN THE KITCHEN FIRST?

35:54.354 --> 35:55.421
OH, REALLY?

35:55.421 --> 35:57.658
YES. BECAUSE IF I CAN'T FIRE
THAT WHORE,

35:57.658 --> 35:59.726
THEN YOU CAN'T FIRE HANNA.
WATCH ME.

35:59.726 --> 36:01.902
THEN YOU BETTER CONTROL
THAT WHORE IN THE KITCHEN

36:01.902 --> 36:04.204
BECAUSE THERE'LL BE ONE HELL
OF A FIRE TO PUT OUT

36:04.204 --> 36:05.338
IF SHE GOES OFF THE RAILS.

36:05.338 --> 36:06.773
AND...

36:06.773 --> 36:10.644
IF SHE CONTINUES
TO DISRESPECT ME IN MY HOME,

36:10.644 --> 36:12.779
NO ARRANGEMENT WILL MATTER.

36:12.779 --> 36:15.582
YOU THINK THESE WHORES
ARE A PROBLEM FOR YOU?

36:15.582 --> 36:17.951
THAT'S BECAUSE
YOU'VE NEVER HAD AN EX‐WIFE.

36:22.556 --> 36:25.592
AND I MEAN IT.

36:35.201 --> 36:36.970
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

36:36.970 --> 36:38.605
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

37:04.437 --> 37:07.641
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

37:07.641 --> 37:08.908
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:08.908 --> 37:10.243
[ LAUGHS ]

37:10.243 --> 37:12.078
I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS.

37:17.050 --> 37:19.753
YEAH?

37:21.354 --> 37:23.056
HI.

37:23.056 --> 37:25.559
I'M SORRY. I'M HERE FROM
JUDGE CRYER'S CAMPAIGN OFFICE.

37:25.559 --> 37:26.827
I HAVE A DELIVERY FOR HIM.

37:26.827 --> 37:28.629
SURE.
DO I NEED TO SIGN FOR IT?

37:30.831 --> 37:34.300
N‐NO. ACTUALLY, I WAS TOLD
I HAVE TO PUT IT IN HIS HANDS.

37:34.300 --> 37:36.637
SURE.

37:36.637 --> 37:38.939
COME ON IN.

37:38.939 --> 37:40.907
DAD!

37:40.907 --> 37:42.108
Jim: YEAH?

37:42.108 --> 37:43.977
WHERE ARE YOU?

37:43.977 --> 37:45.779
IN MY OFFICE.

37:45.779 --> 37:48.114
YOU HAVE A DELIVERY.

37:48.114 --> 37:49.916
JUST RIGHT THROUGH THERE.

37:49.916 --> 37:50.984
THANK YOU.
BRING IT IN.

37:50.984 --> 37:52.018
OFFICE RIGHT THERE, YEAH.

37:52.018 --> 37:53.119
ALL RIGHT.

38:13.313 --> 38:15.816
YEAH. JUST PUT IT
ON THE COFFEE TABLE.

38:15.816 --> 38:18.785
THANK YOU.

38:21.888 --> 38:23.256
WHAT'S GOING ON?

38:23.256 --> 38:26.026
CELINE,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

38:26.026 --> 38:27.427
I'M ‐‐ I'M JUST...

38:27.427 --> 38:29.329
WHAT ‐‐ UM...

38:29.329 --> 38:30.697
I'M GETTING A DELIVERY
FROM MY OFFICE,

38:30.697 --> 38:32.533
BUT I DON'T SEE HOW THAT'S
ANY BUSINESS OF YOURS.

38:32.533 --> 38:35.268
WELL, NO.
NO, SIR.

38:35.268 --> 38:37.103
I JU‐‐
I WAS JUST WONDERING ‐‐

38:37.103 --> 38:38.839
THEN JUST WONDER
SOMEWHERE ELSE.

38:38.839 --> 38:40.040
GET OUT OF MY OFFICE.

38:40.040 --> 38:41.908
CELINE, GO ON. WHAT?
Carlos: HEY, HEY. HEY. HEY.

38:41.908 --> 38:43.343
DON'T TALK TO MY MOTHER
LIKE THAT.

38:43.343 --> 38:45.846
YOUR MOTHER?

38:45.846 --> 38:47.581
[ SPEAKS SPANISH ]

38:49.716 --> 38:52.452
YOU DON'T RECOGNIZE ME?

38:52.452 --> 38:54.487
YOU'RE SOME SNOT‐NOSED
LITTLE KID

38:54.487 --> 38:57.257
THAT USED TO VOLUNTEER
AT MY CAMPAIGN OFFICE.

38:57.257 --> 38:59.125
WHY THE HELL ELSE
SHOULD I RECOGNIZE YOU?

38:59.125 --> 39:02.068
I'M YOUR SON.

39:02.068 --> 39:04.404
SAY THAT AGAIN.

39:04.404 --> 39:06.773
I'M YOUR SON.

39:06.773 --> 39:08.609
CARLOS.

39:19.185 --> 39:21.054
HEY. HEY!

39:22.756 --> 39:24.825
ENGLISH.

39:24.825 --> 39:26.727
PLEASE.

39:26.727 --> 39:29.362
CARLOS.

39:31.031 --> 39:33.233
I SAW YOU ON THE NEWS
DEFENDING YOUR SON.

39:33.233 --> 39:36.970
YOU TALKED ABOUT HOW MUCH
YOU LOVE YOUR FAMILY

39:36.970 --> 39:39.973
AND HOW MUCH
YOU LOVE YOUR SON.

39:39.973 --> 39:42.342
I'M YOUR SON.

39:42.342 --> 39:44.010
I'M YOUR SON, TOO.
WHAT ABOUT ME?

39:44.010 --> 39:46.179
HMM? WHAT ABOUT ME?

39:46.179 --> 39:47.514
IS THAT THE TYPE OF MAN
THAT YOU ARE?

39:47.514 --> 39:49.516
YOU'RE NOT LISTENING TO ME,
PLEASE!

39:49.516 --> 39:51.151
NO, I'M NOT LISTENING
TO YOU ANYMORE, MOM.

39:52.853 --> 39:56.456
I'VE SAT,
AND I'VE WAITED.

39:56.456 --> 39:59.626
AND I'VE WAITED FOR YOU...

40:02.435 --> 40:05.205
...BECAUSE SHE TOLD ME
YOU WERE COMING BACK.

40:05.205 --> 40:07.207
THAT WAS A LONG TIME AGO.

40:07.207 --> 40:09.175
LET IT GO. PLEASE.

40:10.511 --> 40:12.212
YEAH.

40:12.212 --> 40:13.213
PLEASE.

40:13.213 --> 40:15.549
AND I'M STILL WAITING.

40:18.251 --> 40:19.686
LET IT GO.

40:19.686 --> 40:20.954
JUST GO. PLEASE.

40:24.257 --> 40:25.291
JIM.

40:41.274 --> 40:42.308
<i>¿QUé, MAMá?</i>

40:45.612 --> 40:46.847
I HAD TO COME!

40:46.847 --> 40:48.381
WHY? I TOLD YOU!
WHY? BECAUSE.

40:48.381 --> 40:50.684
BECAUSE YOU'RE NOT GONNA MAKE
A MOVE, I'M GONNA DO IT.

40:58.391 --> 41:00.426
MAMá, I'M TIRED WITH IT.
I'M DONE.

41:00.426 --> 41:01.935
I CAN'T KEEP LIVING
THIS LIE.

41:01.935 --> 41:03.637
BUT YOU SHOULD HAVE ASKED ME.
ASKED YOU? FOR WHAT?

41:05.205 --> 41:08.041
THEY ARE NOT LIES, CARLOS!
HUH?

41:08.041 --> 41:10.176
MAMá...

41:10.176 --> 41:11.812
I LOVE YOU,

41:11.812 --> 41:14.615
BUT I CAN'T KEEP LIVING
THIS LIE.

41:16.482 --> 41:19.653
CARLOS.

41:19.653 --> 41:20.987
[ SIGHS ]

41:24.858 --> 41:27.027
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

41:31.698 --> 41:34.334
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:34.334 --> 41:35.702
HOW DID HE KNOW
I WAS HIS FATHER?

41:35.702 --> 41:36.703
Celine:
LOOK AT HIM, JIM.

41:36.703 --> 41:38.805
DO YOU THINK HE'S STUPID?

41:38.805 --> 41:40.674
I DID NOT SLEEP WITH HER.

41:40.674 --> 41:42.142
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.

41:42.142 --> 41:43.877
THAT BOY
DIDN'T KILL THAT BABY.

41:43.877 --> 41:45.579
THEN WHERE IS HE?

41:45.579 --> 41:47.514
WHERE IS SHE?
I DON'T CARE.

41:47.514 --> 41:48.982
[ GRUNTING ]

41:48.982 --> 41:50.551
WHAT HAPPENED?
ASK YOUR DADDY

41:50.551 --> 41:52.018
WHY HE'S BEEN SCREWING
MY GIRL.

41:52.018 --> 41:52.853
WHAT?!

41:52.853 --> 41:53.954
I WANT YOU TO FIND OUT

41:53.954 --> 41:55.088
EVERYTHING YOU CAN
ABOUT THAT BASTARD.

41:55.088 --> 41:57.257
I'M ON IT.

41:57.257 --> 41:58.925
AND IF HE WAS IN PRISON
FOR MURDER,

41:58.925 --> 42:01.768
HOW THE HELL
DID HE GET OUT?!
